ygData.messageBody:
Hello i also am on the bertox server. I play a few diff toons. I have
a 51 druid named Tilari as my main. My alts are 35war named Dorinz
29bard Neranie 10pally Kroaks. I have just recently started my pally
so lately i have been playin him most of the time. Feel free to send
me a tell in game if you wish. On a side note a friend and i are
looking for a guild for our mains I 51 druid him 56 wizard we would
like to get in one with a decent amount of 50 plus chars for groups.
But dont want one to hard core just kind of an easy going guild that
likes to raid and quest and general hunting. So if you know of any
please shoot em my way.
